{"tid":1956596,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】促中共向全球道歉賠償 緬甸總主教︰謊言令數百萬人處危機中","createTime":"2020-04-03T09:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T09:46:31.000Z","uid":70063,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d466cee0884f3c9e49561eb196f41f05b391e888","tid":1956596,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:40:12.000Z","msg":"緬甸仰光總主教貌波（Charles Maung Bo）樞機在天主教亞洲通訊社撰文，促請中共要為武漢肺炎帶來的損失向全球道歉及賠償，並指中共散播的「謊言及政治宣傳令全球數百萬人的性命處於危機之中」。<br />\n<br />\n身兼天主教亞洲主教團協會主席的貌波在文內批評，中共「不近人情及不負責任」的處理肺炎疫情手法，證實過去有關中共政權威脅全球的說法正確。雖然中國過去對全球作出巨大貢獻，但中共政權要為其疏忽過失及遏制手段，導致肺炎疫情今天席捲全球負責。「由集所有權力於一身的習近平及中共控制，而並不是人民把持的中國政權，因為其造成的破壞欠我們所有人一個道歉及賠償。中共至少應撇除其他國家的債務，以抵銷武漢肺炎帶來的經濟壓力。為我們所有人著想，我們不能懼怕向（中共）政權問責」。<br />\n<br />\n貌波又批評中共的人權紀錄，指「中國近年嚴厲打壓言論自由，律師、博客、異見人士、民權分子都被拘捕甚示被消失。尤其中國打壓不同宗教，破壞許多教堂及設集中營扣押超過100萬維吾爾人...曾經是全亞洲最開放城市之一的香港，自由、人權及法治亦受嚴重侵蝕」。<br />\n<br />\n貌波再三強調要為今次疫情負上最大責任者是中共政權，並非中國人，「我澄清中共應為此負責，但不是中國人，任何人都不應因為今次危機仇視中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200402/5OXP3ODPRIDYG4DB5JIS5WCP5U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1dOcWNQA_BTwGC6aqr3uTdXTcjYAapn1dEAhQLwlWD5pqlL2F9m-dLfNY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200402%2F5OXP3ODPRIDYG4DB5JIS5WCP5U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1dOcWNQA_BTwGC6aqr3uTdXTcjYAapn1dEAhQLwlWD5pqlL2F9m-dLfNY&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BvrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=a0c88e75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200402%2F5OXP3ODPRIDYG4DB5JIS5WCP5U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1dOcWNQA_BTwGC6aqr3uTdXTcjYAapn1dEAhQLwlWD5pqlL2F9m-dLfNY&h=85c78cb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200402/5OXP3ODPRIDYG4DB5JIS5WCP5U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1dOcWNQA_BTwGC6aqr3uTdXTcjYAapn1dEAhQLwlWD5pqlL2F9m-dLfNY</a>"},{"pid":"9e21b658a191da1ba2256321ddff37e25bb9b198","tid":1956596,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efebcc8c9e45d31968666451338a37b60977146e","tid":1956596,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:46:30.000Z","msg":"個主教識玩<br />\n將國同黨分開來講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01c485b0d4c9c05c851f9d4a63bf98f7701d532","tid":1956596,"uid":61235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"證據?<br />\n拎李文亮單野出黎就夠收班小粉紅皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}